Package GameServer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bullet
    Presents one bullet in the online with all its features such as location , speed , time handling and image file .
    Game
    Handles all important elements of an online game .
    GameHandler
    Handles the game in server .
    GameLoop
    A very simple structure for the main game loop.
    GameServer
    Server for the game in online games .
    GameServerMain
    Main class for game server .
    Information
    Consists of all information that the server sends .
    MapHandler  
    QueueHandler  
    SocketHandler  
    Tank
    Simulation of tank in the game consisting of all of its components such as location , bullets , moveThread and speed .
    Wall
    A wall piece object in the game which consists of its location start and ending point , its lives , type ( which is smp or brk ) and lineType which means if it is horizontal or vertical .
